## Client Gating Pattern

```tsx
// Pull can() from useAppShell — no separate import needed
const { can } = useAppShell();

// Gate rendering
{can('skills:manage') && <ManageSkillsButton />}

// Gate navigation
if (!can('admin:roles')) return <Navigate to="/" />;
```

## When to Load the Skill

Load the `rbac-management` skill (`.cursor/skills/rbac-management/SKILL.md`) when:
- A new permission key must be added (migration + middleware + client wiring)
- An orphaned key must be removed (migration + cleanup)
- Role-permission assignments need updating
